items.name: NXP LPC800-MAX
items.text_description: LPC800-MAX from NXP is an mbed enabled platform which combines the advantages of the mbed ecosystem and Arduino form factor.

items.name: Seeeduino-Arch
items.text_description: Seeeduino Arch from Seeed Studio is an mbed enabled development board which combines some advantages of mbed and Arduino. Arch is based on NXP LPC11U24 with Arduino form factor and Grove connectors. Building a prototype is easy with lots of Shield and Grove modules.

items.name: ARM Cortex-M Prototyping System (MPS2)
items.text_description: The Cortex-M Prototyping System (or V2M-MPS2) is designed for prototyping and evaluation Cortex-M family of processors. It is an affordable motherboard available as part of the Versatile Express range of development boards. It boasts a large FPGA for prototyping Cortex-M based designs and a range of different debug options. It comes with a range of useful peripherals including PSRAM, Ethernet, touch screen, Audio, VGA, SPI and GPIO. It comes provided with fixed encrypted FPGA implementations of all the Cortex-M processors.The product supports Cortex-M0 design start and includes an example design with CMSDK peripherals which the user can use in their design. It is an ideal platform for the evaluation and FPGA prototyping of Cortex-M based designs.

items.name: Seeed Bluetooth Shield
items.text_description: The Bluetooth Shield integrates a Serial Bluetooth module. It can be easily used with mbed/Arduino for transparent wireless serial communication.

items.name: DisplayModule 2.4" 240x320 Touch TFT with 8-bit Interface
items.text_description: The DM-TFT24-104 display module, specifications and other resources are available from DisplayModule.com.

items.name: EA LPC11U35 QuickStart Board
items.text_description: The LPC11U35 QuickStart Board from Embedded Artists is a easy to use ARM Cortex-M0 rapid prototyping board in a breadboard-friendly 30-pin DIL format. The board targets smaller control applications as well as low-power applications. The small form factor makes the board perfect for integration.

items.name: X-NUCLEO-IKS01A1 - Motion MEMS and Environmental Sensors
items.text_description: The X-NUCLEO-IKS01A1 is a motion MEMS and environmental sensor evaluation board system.
